text: Craftsman Home, 40x60 Shop on 10 acres...Picture a cozy living room with a river rock fireplace, sunlight streaming through high windows, and hickory floors leading to a kitchen adorned with alder cabinets. This home is a harmonious blend of natural materials and thoughtful design. The home is 2736 sq ft, 3 bdrms, 2 bths, on upper floor, den/office, 3/4 bthrm, spacious dining rm, kitchen with granite counters, eating bar & walk-in pantry on main floor. Unfinished bonus room over garage has future access from upstairs hall. Shop has additional studio space, full bthrm, loft storage area & 3 bays w/14' doors. Private setting, garden space, partially fenced & convenient to I-5.

ATTENTION INVESTORS! An exceptional opportunity awaits in the heart of Concrete. Nestled within this 1, 508 sq. ft. Residence is a 3 bedrooms and 1 full bath, perfect for comfortable living. Additionally, the 1, 196 sq. ft. basement, cleverly doubling as a garage, offers ample space for expansion. Complementing the garage, discover multiple bonus areas and a convenient .25 bath, providing versatility and potential. All plumbing was updated roughly 5 years ago. Embrace this chance to unleash your creativity and restore this turn-of-the-century gem to its former glory. Discover the epitome of coastal living at this Samish Island home, on the market for the first time. Nestled on 1/3 acre with low-bank waterfront, this residence offers a harmonious blend of tranquility and comfort. Step inside to find a well maintained home with gorgeous views of the bay. Hosting guests is a delight with a thoughtfully designed guest room downstairs, ensuring privacy and comfort. Step out to your beach with a private dock, and a 17' 1995 Grady White boat included in the sale! Plenty of storage in the spacious 2 car garage with a separate entrance to a storage loft above. Embrace the serenity of island living and create unforgettable memories in this waterfront sanctuary!

Buildable lot in the middle of Mount Vernon, close to the Kulshan Trail and Madison Elementary School. Just received lot certification from the City. Approval good for 2 years per the City (see attached decision.) Water, power, sewer, and gas are all in the street. Lot is mostly level with large cedar trees. Seller will consider a short term owner/contract or cash out subject to construction loan.

Looking for private area, no HOA, lots of parking & a Shop? This 3 bedroom home is located near end of private lane in great location between Burlington & Sedro. Front yard w/ mature landscaping, garden area. Parking in front & back of home, side, driveway & across lane. Large fully fenced back yard w/ det garage/shop, carport & greenhouse area. Shop has power, heat, piping for woodstove. Recent updates in home include mini-split heat pump/AC, tankless water heater, new lighting/ceiling fans, custom blinds & some flooring. Kitchen w/plenty of cupboards & garden window. Converted garage adds extra living space. Utility area/mud entry off side of home. Plenty of room to spread out. Conveniently located by all amenities & I-5.

Enjoy water, island & ferry views from this nearly new home located in desirable 48 North. This 5 br 2 story home has 9 ft ceilings on both levels & over 3, 100 sf of open concept living plus 3-car garage. Hardwood floors lead to a light & airy kitchen. Granite counters, dbl oven range, under cabinet lighting, microwave & walk-in pantry. Main floor has flex rm closed off by pocket doors, hearth rm w/gas FP, 5th bdrm/office plus 3/4 bth. Upstairs find the primary bdrm w/luxury bth & heated tile floor, additional 3 bdrms plus bath w/dbl sinks, laundry rm & family rm w/kitchenette. Watch breathtaking sunsets from the covered deck. Fully fenced private backyard, convenient walkout patio, irrigated landscaping. HOA. Move in ready!

Charming 1920's home with modern updates nestled in the heart of Lyman on a large in-town lot. This 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence offers a blend of vintage character and contemporary conveniences.Located on a quiet dead-end street, the property has a large spacious backyard that holds endlesspossibilities. Inside, you'll find a primary bedroom with an ensuite bathroom and a walk-in closet. The openconcept living room and kitchen create a welcoming atmosphere, perfect for entertaining. A utility roomprovides convenient access to the back porch, enhancing the home's functionality. Recent updates of anewer roof, septic system, & fencing will ensure peace of mind for years to come. Schedule a showing today, beforeit is gone!

Master bedroom with private bathroom.Walk out your back door onto your back deck looking out into own private oasis in your back yard.backyard is fully fenced . Stunning two bedroom, two bathroom condo in the Stonebridge Active Adult Community. This home features numerous updates, including hardwood floors, modern lighting, stylish backsplash's, custom closet organization, new counters, sinks, fixtures, newer appliances, and plantation shutters. With vaulted ceilings and an open concept floor plan, the home feels fresh and spacious. The kitchen offers ample counter space, a new single basin sink, a walk-in pantry, and sleek modern appliances. Spacious bedrooms are enhanced with new closet systems for optimal organization. The HOA covers yard and structure maintenance, a clubhouse, walking trails and RV storage available. Located in a quiet cul-de-sac, close to amenities and medical facilities.

Welcome to your next home in a fantastic location! This property features 4 bedrooms & a large, almost fully fenced yard, perfect for many buyers. The upper level boasts a spacious living room, kitchen, dining area, balcony for entertaining, 2 bedrooms, & 1 bathroom. The lower level offers two additional bedrooms, a half bath, utility area & storage closet. Oversized single-car garage provides ample storage space & backyard access, while large deck above ideal for BBQs & relaxing. Recent updates include relatively new metal garage door & fresh paint on house 4-5 years ago. There's also a convenient storage shed located on the south side of the property. Close location to all essential services, this home offers both comfort & convenience.

Must see condominium with incredible! amazing! views. Balcony is perfect for entertaining (plumbed for gas grill) Cherry wood and slate floors, walk thru master closet (back entrance to laundry room), upgraded wood/granite built-ins in serving pantry; state of the art appliances, shower with view & more! Video monitored security & alarm systems. This unit is exceptional! Entertainment center and TV stay, dual head shower with view & more! End unit with Shannon Pt. as neighbor means wooded park like setting. Video monitored security & alarm systems. This unit is exceptional! Other items are negotiable.

This historic, architecturally designed, 1919 Hollywood bungalow style home is such an eye catcher! Designed with thought and intention this home has more than its share of character, such as terrazzo porch, mosaic tile entry, old growth fir floors with cherry wood inlay border and an inglenook with custom stained glass windows by artist, Jack Archibald! The living and dining rooms are inviting with large windows that allow abundant light and look out over the mature landscaping. There are two large bedrooms on the main floor and the inglenook which could be used as another bedroom. The partially finished basement has room for a 3rd bedroom, shop, huge laundry room, 1/2 bath and tons of storage. You will love the vintage charm in this home!

Beautiful 2BR, 1.75BA condo in lovely 55 & Better community offers the very best in serene living! So many features to love - new vinyl plank floors, heat pump for cooling, single-level layout w/vaulted ceilings in the living rm and cozy gas fireplace. Your primary suite with attached bath features a spacious walk-in closet + an extra private feel with views of the trees & greenbelt behind. The front porch & partially covered back deck are the best seats in the house for enjoying the surrounding nature, the neighboring creek and water feature views. 2-car garage offers plenty of storage space for hobbies. Great location near medical and shopping yet private and quiet - there's even a community trail with private gate leading to Haggen.

Welcome to La Conner Heights, a collection of high-end custom homes built by award-winning builder BYK. Set in the heart of Historic La Conner, perched on a cul-de-sac with 360 views of quilted farmlands, majestic Mt Baker, the Cascades & sparkling Salish Seas. Home features 2, 610 SF of designer finishes, soaring ceilings, walls of windows, gleaming wood floors & main level living. Chefs kitchen with high-end appliances opens to welcoming gathering spaces. 2 primary suites with luxurious baths, plus 2 add'l BRs. Spacious bonus room could be 5th BR. Stroll to downtown La Conner's vibrant art scene, boutique shopping, farm to table dining & acclaimed marina, your gateway to the San Juan Islands. Easy I-5 access to Seattle & Vancouver BC.

$40K PRICE IMPROVEMENT! QUALIFIED BUYER MAY ASSUME MORTGAGE AT 2.5% INTEREST, PENDING APPROVAL. Relax & relish the stylish & effortless lifestyle at Woodside, Mount Vernon's Premier 55+ community. The stunning Chestnut floorplan boasts numerous custom designer upgrades. Savor the open floorplan, Living/Dining & gourmet Kitchen w/upgraded SS appliances & finishes you've always coveted. The main floor primary suite features a luxurious 4-piece bath/walk-in closet. Upper level Bonus Room w/ adjoining bed/bath, ideal for crafts or company. A third bedroom/office on the Main. Stay comfortable w/Gas fireplace & Central A/C. Fully fenced yard w patio & remote canopy. Amenities include clubhouse, parks, trails & HOA maintained front/back yards.

Unobstructed views of Sauk Mountain on over 5 acre awaits your vision. This mostly level lot is partial treed with easy access. Only minutes from the beautiful Skagit river and state parks, this is a wonderful spot to enjoy the peace and tranquility of the great outdoors. Weather you want to hunt, fish, or hike this is a beautiful spot to create the haven you've been looking for. Get your piece of the beautiful North Cascade corridor today!

Amazing investment opportunity situated on an expansive 13, 000+ square foot lot with R3 Zoning. This well-cared-for craftsman home offers multiple options for creative ownership. Rent both units or occupy one as a primary residence and rent the other for income. A third option would be to subdivide the property and develop each parcel to maximize lot density. Infrastructure upgrades include a newer roof and windows, updated furnace, plumbing, and electrical. The property offers lovely living spaces including a main-level primary bedroom/bathroom and office, along with a functional floorplan with great ambient light. Timeless details and millwork add to the charm of this classic home. A generous-sized basement awards storage and utility.

Nestled on the canal with marina, mountain, and golf course vistas, this home boasts stunning landscapes adorned with mature plants and winding walkways, offering a serene oasis. Picture windows frame stunning views from nearly every room, bathing the home with natural light and inviting nature indoors. Enjoy the seamless flow of the open-concept layout, featuring hardwood floors throughout the living, dining, and kitchen areas, perfect for effortless entertaining. Relax by the cozy fireplace in the family room, or step outside onto the spacious deck to soak in the panoramic scenery, creating moments of tranquility and connection with nature. Shelter Bay amenities include marinas, sports courts, 3 par golf course, beach access & a pool!

Discover a prime opportunity to own nearly 40 acres in South Skagit. This expansive property carries dual zoning designations, offering both agricultural and recreational possibilities. Enjoy the rural setting with picturesque views of the Cascade Mountains, with quick easy access to all the amenities of town. This parcel is perfect for farmers, investors, or those looking to build a custom farmstead amidst natural beauty. No studies have been performed on the property and is being sold As-Is as part of an estate sale.

Rare lot in the city of Sedro Woolley, with all utilities on site. Condemned home on property may be salvageable. Great location and level lot, ready for your vision. Seller/builder has conceptual drawings for a mixed commercial/apartment style building and will work with buyer should they want to pursue this avenue. City of SW prefers this type of structure but has indicated they will allow the current home to be rehabbed. Buyer to verify potential uses and zoning with the city of Sedro Woolley.

Bring your imagination. This property provides the most tranquil setting. Enjoy all nature has to offer on your private 6.2 acres. This 1995 manufactured home has plenty of space, with well-sized bedrooms and two full baths. The kitchen provides a large eating area. The front deck provides plenty of room for entertainment. There is a 20X30 metal shop with a metal roof that includes a 10X10 backroom with a bath. The property also boasts a woodshed, gazebo, play equipment and a chicken coop. There are great recreational areas nearby, and only a short drive to the town of Sedro-Wooley and all the conveniences. Welcome Home!

Beautifully maintained 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home with 1, 704 square feet of comfortable living space nestled in a desirable neighborhood. Primary suite with attached bathroom and walk-in closet. Inviting living room featuring a vaulted ceiling and a cozy fireplace. Oak hardwood floors, open floor plan, 2 car garage, large deck. Ample backyard space, perfect for those who love gardening or entertaining outdoors. Large shed for your gardening/yard tools. Make this dream home yours!

Located in the desirable Cedar Heights community is this impeccably maintained 3 bed/2.5 bath home! Welcomed by a covered front porch, the main floor features fresh paint throughout. The entry and den leads to open concept dining, family room & kitchen with stainless steel appliances, newer granite countertops, sink and updated flooring throughout. Through the slider is the beautifully landscaped and private fully-fenced backyard including covered deck for entertaining! Laundry room located across from the guest bath and 2-car garage access nearby. Upstairs you are greeted with the spacious primary bedroom with jetted tub and large walk-in closet. Second full bath and 2 more bedrooms with beautiful mountainous views! Welcome Home!

Discover this extraordinary custom-built luxury home, featuring 3461 sqft on a half-acre landscaped lot offering privacy and Northwest living. The main floor boasts a spacious open great room with vaulted ceilings, skylights, and expansive views. The chef's kitchen includes custom cabinets, pull-outs, under-counter lighting, a custom tile backsplash, a walk-in pantry. The primary suite offers a grand custom tile shower, spacious walk-in closet, and champagne bronze fixtures. Downstairs features a media room, office, full bath, and flex room/ 4th bedroom. Outside, enjoy a fenced yard with a covered heated patio, gas BBQ, fire pit, and fenced yard. Includes a massive four-car garage. Ideal for luxury seekers in a serene setting.

Discover the perfect spot for your camper, RV, or a manufactured home in the Cape Horn community. This versatile lot is ideal for year-round living or as a weekend getaway. With water and electricity conveniently available at the street, setting up is a breeze. Enjoy easy access to the stunning Skagit River, perfect for fishing enthusiasts and nature lovers. The community park enhances your experience with amenities like a playground, a gazebo with picnic tables, a basketball court, making it perfect for gatherings and leisurely activities. Explore the numerous nearby trails and immerse yourself in the natural beauty of the Pacific NW. Build your dream home & savor all that this enchanting location has to offer. Your adventure begins here!
